OL,5, A funeral director is calling for more 
OL,6, environmentally-friendly methods of    
OL,7, body disposal to be legalised.         
OL,9,FAndrew Purves said traditional fire    
OL,10,Fcremation used a lot of energy and that
OL,11,Fground was becoming scarce for burials.
OL,13,FHe said people needed more choice and  
OL,14,Fthat alternatives like water cremation 
OL,15,Fand human composting should be allowed 
OL,16,Fin the UK.                             
OL,18,FThe Scottish government said it wanted 
OL,19,Fto allow water cremation and would be  
OL,20,Flaunching a consultation on the issue. 
